post.description:
If you are registered partner of Merk you can leverage this method to register users into Merk.

If you want to become a partner contact us at [podpora@merk.cz](mailto:podpora@merk.cz)

API validates:

* `partner_code`
* `email` format
* `territory`/`regno`: checks if company with provided `regno` and `territory` exists

**Example responses:**

`HTTP 200`, User is registered:

    {
        "login_email": "abcd@example.com",
        "password": "someRand0mPwd",
        "api_key": "asdfedeASAD1234AdasdaBla"
    }

`HTTP 400 Bad Request`, Not found company (regno + territory):

    {
        "non_field_errors": [
        "No such company found, please enter proper Reg. no."
        ]
    }

`HTTP 202 Accepted`, dry-run:

    {
        "detail": "Validation successful. But dry run requested, no user created."
    }

`HTTP 403 Forbidden`, Registration disabled:

    {
        "detail": "User registration is currently disabled."
    }

This endpoint is throttled to **40 requests per minute**.
